%N A331671 Number of Pythagorean triangles with sum of legs n.
%H A331671 Ray Chandler, <a href="/A331671/b331671.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..10000</a>
%F A331671 a(n) = Sum_{k=1..floor((n-1)/2)} c(sqrt((n-k)^2+k^2)), where c(n) = 1-ceiling(n)+floor(n). - _Wesley Ivan Hurt_, Jun 26 2026
%t A331671 Table[Sum[1 - Ceiling[Sqrt[(n - k)^2 + k^2]] + Floor[Sqrt[(n - k)^2 + k^2]], {k, Floor[(n - 1)/2]}], {n, 100}] (* _Wesley Ivan Hurt_, Jun 26 2026 *)
